311
00:30:29,954 --> 00:30:31,121
Itu pilihan saya.

312
00:30:43,467 --> 00:30:45,886
<i>Orang yang berada</i>
<i>dalam keadaan sangat terdesak tahu</i>

313
00:30:47,054 --> 00:30:48,389
<i>bahawa nasib malang</i>

314
00:30:48,472 --> 00:30:51,934
<i>akan mengekori mereka</i>
<i>yang tak memiliki apa-apa.</i>

315
00:30:52,643 --> 00:30:55,771
<i>Hutang lintah darah ayah saya</i>
<i>asyik meningkat</i>

316
00:30:56,355 --> 00:30:58,148
<i>dan tiada jalan penyelesaian</i>

317
00:30:59,441 --> 00:31:00,401
<i>sehingga dia mati.</i>

318
00:31:02,528 --> 00:31:03,529
Pergi tonton filem.

319
00:31:05,197 --> 00:31:06,824
Kamu kata teringin nak tengok.

320
00:31:11,245 --> 00:31:12,288
Jumpa nanti.

321
00:31:15,457 --> 00:31:16,292
<i>Satu hari,</i>

322
00:31:16,875 --> 00:31:19,670
<i>mak saya paksa saya keluar</i>
<i>untuk tonton filem.</i>

323
00:31:24,550 --> 00:31:25,759
<i>Ada sesuatu yang tak kena.</i>

324
00:31:25,843 --> 00:31:27,136
AYAM DUMARI

325
00:31:29,346 --> 00:31:31,265
<i>Saya guna duit itu untuk beli ayam goreng.</i>

326
00:31:35,311 --> 00:31:38,397
<i>Apabila tiba ke rumah,</i>
<i>ibu bapa saya dah minum racun perosak</i>

327
00:31:42,693 --> 00:31:44,528
<i>dan gasolin dah dituang di atas lantai.</i>

328
00:31:48,365 --> 00:31:51,452
<i>Saya tahu mereka cuba</i>
<i>jadikan kebakaran itu seperti kemalangan.</i>

329
00:32:17,853 --> 00:32:19,897
Saya nak mati bersama mereka…

330
00:32:23,692 --> 00:32:25,069
