349
00:34:41,580 --> 00:34:45,375
Ya, Polis Cheongun dah periksa tempat itu,
tapi tiada apa-apa yang mencurigakan.

350
00:34:47,836 --> 00:34:50,672
Situasi di lokasi mungkin berbeza.
Kita pergi ke sana.

351
00:34:53,717 --> 00:34:54,718
Helo.

352
00:34:56,303 --> 00:34:57,471
Sang-mi.

353
00:34:58,263 --> 00:35:01,433
Awak yang uruskan
pembekal ruang simpanan luar kita, bukan?

354
00:35:01,517 --> 00:35:02,643
Ya.

355
00:35:02,726 --> 00:35:05,187
Tolong hantar senarainya sekarang.

356
00:35:05,270 --> 00:35:06,980
Okey. Saya terus hantar.

357
00:35:12,361 --> 00:35:15,197
STATUS KONTRAK
PEMBEKAL RUANG SIMPANAN LUAR

358
00:35:23,372 --> 00:35:24,414
<i>Datang ke lokasi ini.</i>

359
00:35:33,090 --> 00:35:34,967
Awak perlu hubungi pembekal?

360
00:35:37,928 --> 00:35:39,847
Kita boleh tahu butiran karya

361
00:35:39,930 --> 00:35:42,558
