beli lukisan yang dia mahu.

374
00:36:42,159 --> 00:36:43,076
Betul.

375
00:36:43,911 --> 00:36:47,789
Sama macam belanjakan puluhan juta won

376
00:36:47,873 --> 00:36:49,374
untuk beli beg mewah seperti itu.

377
00:36:52,336 --> 00:36:55,714
Orang begitu bangga apabila dipilih

378
00:36:55,797 --> 00:36:58,967
