Saya daripada Royal Auction.

406
00:39:40,879 --> 00:39:42,005
Katarina?

407
00:39:42,798 --> 00:39:44,591
Ia ada banyak isu kecil.

408
00:39:45,842 --> 00:39:47,636
Walaupun bersaiz besar,

409
00:39:47,719 --> 00:39:49,930
